OL,3,CDriver went into 'blind panic' after
OL,4,Chitting pedestrian and drove off
OL,6,FA driver who hit a pedestrian and
OL,7,Fbroke their leg went into a "blind
OL,8,Fpanic" and drove away from the scene,
OL,9,Fa court has heard.
OL,11,FLiam Davies, 29, turned into Rhyl High
OL,12,FStreet and hit Susan Butterworth in
OL,13,FOctober last year but failed to stop
OL,14,Fafter seriously injuring her.
OL,16,FDavies admitted to causing serious
OL,17,Finjury by driving without due care and
OL,18,Fattention and received a suspended
OL,19,Fjail sentence at Llandudno
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court.
