OL,3,CDriver went into 'blind panic' after
OL,4,Chitting pedestrian and drove off
OL,6,FThe prosecution told the court that
OL,7,FDavies was driving along Wellington
OL,8,FRoad before turning onto the town
OL,9,Fcentre high street and colliding with
OL,10,FMrs Butterworth.
OL,12,Fthe 29-year-old then failed to stop
OL,13,Fand it was members of the public that
OL,14,Fcame to the aid of Mrs Butterworth and
OL,15,Fgave first aid.
OL,17,FPolice were called and officers took
OL,18,FMrs Butterworth, who is retired, to
OL,19,FYsbyty Glan Clwyd in Bodelwyddan for
OL,20,Ftreatment. Davies drove home and was
OL,21,Farrested later.
