OL,4,Chitting pedestrian and drove off
OL,6,FIn a victim statement Mrs Butterworth
OL,7,Fdescribed her injuries, explaining she
OL,8,Fhas sustained cuts, fractured her
OL,9,Fright knee twice and fractured her
OL,10,Fright femur. She was also concussed
OL,11,Ffollowing the incident. She had to
OL,12,Fwear a cast and leg brace for eight
OL,13,Fweeks.
OL,15,FShe said: "The driver should have
OL,16,Fstopped and checked on me - that would
OL,17,Fhave meant a lot to me."
