OL,4,Chitting pedestrian and drove off
OL,6,FShe added that since being hit, she is
OL,7,Fnervous any time a vehicle is close to
OL,8,Fher and her family have had to step in
OL,9,Fto help her with shopping.
OL,11,FNia Dawson, defending Davies, said:
OL,12,F"He went through a green light (and)
OL,13,Fthe lady stepped onto the road. He
OL,14,Fshould have seen her.
OL,16,F"The weather conditions were really
OL,17,Fbad. He has flashbacks wishing he had
OL,18,Fseen her and this would never have
OL,19,Fhappened."
