OL,3,CDriver went into 'blind panic' after
OL,4,Chitting pedestrian and drove off
OL,6,FShe added that Davies had been under a
OL,7,F"particularly great amount of stress"
OL,8,Fand had been on his way to collect
OL,9,Fmedication.J"He thinks that's why he
OL,10,Fdid not do the right thing and stop,"
OL,11,Fshe said.
OL,13,F"He knows in his heart that he should
OL,14,Fhave stopped. He was in a blind panic."
OL,16,FShe also said that the fact that the
OL,17,Fcase has taken as long as eleven
OL,18,Fmonths to come to court "beggars
OL,19,Fbelief". Today the court also heard
OL,20,Fthat Davies was given a community
OL,21,Forder in June for a common assault.
