OL,6,FThe court heard Davies is making
OL,7,Fprogress on that community order.
OL,9,FDavies was given a 16-week jail term,
OL,10,Fsuspended for 18 months. He must
OL,11,Fcomplete 100 hours of unpaid work and
OL,12,Fattend 40 hours of rehabilitation
OL,13,Factivity. He must also pay #85 costs
OL,14,Fand a #154 surcharge and was
OL,15,Fdisqualified from driving for 18
OL,16,Fmonths.
